Simphiwe Ngema has supposed been asked to marry one of the Masilela brothers Simphiwe Ngema&#8217;s broken heart is about to be mend. The young Widow who lost her husband a few weeks ago and is to wed again.Simphiwe and Dumi got married early this year and he unfortunately couldn&#8217;t stay to enjoy his marriage. The Ngema and Masilela family came to an agreement that one of Dumi&#8217;s brothers will marry Simphiwe. The reason to their agreement isn&#8217;t to fulfill tradition but to fulfill the Masilela family&#8217;s promise to take care of Simphiwe to the very end